OL,5,G2130 1976: Summer of... Heat
OL,6,     FDocumentary looking at the
OL,7,     Fheatwave of 1976. As the country
OL,8,     Fsweltered, tensions rose. Contains
OL,9,     Fvery strong language.
OL,10,G2230 The World About Us: The Year of
OL,11,G     the Ladybirds
OL,12,     FDocumentary exploring the long,
OL,13,     Fhot summer of 1976, the driest for
OL,14,     Ftwo centuries. It was seen by many
OL,15,     Fas a year of disaster for the
OL,16,     Fcountryside. But was it really?
OL,17,G2320 Horizon Special: The Great British
OL,18,G     Drought
OL,19,     FDocumentary that goes behind the
OL,20,     Fscenes to explore the drought
OL,21,     Fcrisis of 1976.
